pr_title: ðŸ“Š Implement new Sugarizer Chart activity
pr_body:
## Chart Activity
### Feature To be Implemented:
-  [x] Activity UI
-  [x] Ability to input data to make different charts.
-  [x] Add/Remove data from chart.
-  [x] Swap Chart Fields.
-  [x] Config Palette to modify chart colors and axis labels.
-  [x] Font Palette to change font-family & size of labels & title.
-  [x] Horizontal , line & Pie charts.
-  [x] Full-screen Mode.
-  [x] Add activity Tutorial.
-  [x] Save in Journal.
-  [x] update activity description in locale.ini !
-  [x] Localization.
-  [x] Export Chart as image and CSV.
-  [x] Read data from Measure & Stopwatch activity !
-  [x] Read CSV file to make a Chart.(Support CSV in Journal & CSV Viewer)
-  [x] Share the activity !

#### Please review the completed features marked with checkmarks and provide your suggestions and feedback. Thank you!
---
